snippet.title: Vengeance of Excalibur gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Vengeance of Excalibur, Dos PC game produced by Synergistic Software in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/vengeance-of-excalibur/5000/
Watching the intro and exploring in this Athurian fantasy adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
